text: Eching is a municipality in the district of Freising, in Upper Bavaria, Germany. ==Geography== Eching is 18 km north of Munich (centre) and 15 km southwest of Freising. ==Districts== The municipality Eching has existed since 1978 and consists of Eching, Günzenhausen, Ottenburg, Deutenhausen, Dietersheim and Gut Hollern. Hollern (to the west of the federal road B 13) has been incorporated with Unterschleißheim since 1990. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official homepage Category:Freising (district)
